
 if you have ant (http://www.apache.org) installed just run "ant" 


 or use the compile script:
  ./compile.sh


 watch out: this script has to be made executable with the chmod u+x command...




 or compile it manually:

 javac org\columba\main\Main.java 
 javac org\columba\gui\themes\*.java
 javac org\columba\gui\themes\thincolumba\*.java
 javac org\columba\gui\themes\contrastcolumba\*.java
 javac org\columba\folder\*.java
 javac org\columba\folder\columba\*.java 
 javac org\columba\folder\encryption\*.java 
 javac org\columba\folder\gui\*.java 
 javac org\columba\folder\imap\*.java 
 javac org\columba\folder\outbox\*.java
 javac org\columba\folder\temp\*.java 
 javac org\columba\folder\virtual\*.java 
 javac org\columba\pop3\*.java


 JDK1.3 users need to adjust their classpath in order to
 compile Columba. See the README_JDK1.3 for more information.

